BusinessTech is the best place to reach South Africa’s business decision makers, thanks to its position as the largest business news website in the country. It is the first website C-level executives, business owners, company directors, managers, and professionals visit each day – and is often the last website they visit before logging off at night. BusinessTech is read by over 7 million people each month. A breakdown of BusinessTech’s monthly South African audience is detailed below. Junior Management – 1,085,058
Middle Management – 1,331,807
Business Owner – 856,971
Senior Management – 712,260
CEO/Director – 131,809 These readers are highly influential in terms of purchasing decisions their businesses make, thanks to their positions of authority. This makes BusinessTech an obvious choice for companies who want to run effective online B2B advertising campaigns. BusinessTech offers a range of advertising options which makes it easy to reach our influential audience. This includes sponsored articles with social media amplification, display banners, video interviews, dedicated mailers, and more. BusinessTech’s marketing team also takes care of all aspects of an advertising campaign – from content creation, to targeting, to execution, to performance reports. To find out more about advertising on BusinessTech, click here.